To Use:

Salesforce:
Create Salesforce outbound message with a minimum of two fields
 - Id (This will exist by default)
 - Payload__c

Set enpoint to ngrok url routed to the /obm directory
 - ex: https://9b6d6a1d.ngrok.io/obm

Trigger the outbound message using a Workflow Action

Node: 
Install required packages using "npm install <package-name>"
Install ngrok
	- run "ngrok.exe http 80"

run "node app.js"
